        "comment": {
            "name": "comment",
            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/42526",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=digitalstruct",
                        "name": "digitalstruct",
                        "displayName": "Mike Willbanks",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Usage:\r\n\r\nConfiguration INI File (for Zend_Application):\r\nresources.session.saveHandler.class        = Zend_Session_SaveHandler_Cache\r\n\r\nBootstrap.php (for Zend_Application):\r\n{noformat}\r\n    protected function _initSessionCache()\r\n        $this->bootstrap('session');\r\n        $opts = $this->getOptions();\r\n        if ('Zend_Session_SaveHandler_Cache' == $opts['resources']['session']['saveHandler']['class']) {\r\n            $cache = $this->bootstrap('cachemanager')\r\n                          ->getResource('cachemanager')\r\n                          ->getCache('memcached');\r\n            Zend_Session::getSaveHandler()->setCache($cache);\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n{noformat}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=digitalstruct",
                        "name": "digitalstruct",
                        "displayName": "Mike Willbanks",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-10-15T11:05:17.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-10-15T11:05:56.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/42540",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ramon",
                        "name": "ramon",
                        "displayName": "Ramon Henrique Ornelas",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Hi Mike\r\n\r\nThere a need of elaborate a propose, but already exists a porpose to this component http:\/\/framework.zend.com\/wiki\/display\/ZFPROP\/Zend_Session_SaveHandler_Cache+-+Nick+Daugherty.\r\n\r\nI have a code similar the this but propose only would accepted until final of August. \r\n\r\nAlso Zend_Session in ZF2 has changes and Zend_Cache is in phase refactoring.\r\n\r\nGreetings\r\nRamon",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ramon",
                        "name": "ramon",
                        "displayName": "Ramon Henrique Ornelas",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-10-17T05:21:11.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-10-17T05:21:11.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/42574",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "For the record: the SaveHandler functionality in ZF2 is not much changed, if at all, as it simply provides an interface for building a component that works with session_set_save_handler.\r\n\r\nMike -- I'd forgotten about the cache savehandler, and that it was already accepted. Closing this issue, as it will be implemented for ZF2.",
